text: Graham Lee Rennison (born 2 October 1978) is an English former professional footballer who played as a defender in the Football League for York City, and in non-League football for Whitby Town. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:People from Northallerton Category:Sportspeople from Yorkshire Category:English footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:York City F.C. players Category:Whitby Town F.C. players Category:English Football League players
